@@JvWizardDrawBorderEdges
<TITLE JvWizardDrawBorderEdges function>
Summary
  Draw borders on a canvas.
Description
  Use JvWizardDrawBorderEdges as a convenient way of drawing border edges on a canvas.
Parameters
  ACanvas - The canvas to draw on.
  ABounds - The rect to draw in.
  AStyle  - The style to use.
  AEdges  - Edges to draw.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@JvWizardDrawEdges
<TITLE JvWizardDrawEdges function>
Summary
  Draw edges on a canvas.
Description
  Use JvWizardDrawEdges as a convenient way to draw edges on a canvas.
Parameters
  ACanvas - The canvas to draw on.
  ABounds - The rect to draw in.
  ULColor - Color of left and upper edge.
  LRColor - Color of right and bottom edge.
  AEdges  - Edges to draw.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@JvWizardDrawImage
<TITLE JvWizardDrawImage procedure>
Summary
  Draws an image on a canvas.
Description
  Use JvWizardDrawImage as a convenient way of drawing an image on a canvas.
Parameters
  ACanvas  - The canvas to draw on.
  AGraphic - The image to draw.
  ARect    - The area in the canvas to draw in.
  Align    - The alignment of the image.
  ALayout  - The layout of the image.

