@@TJvWizardImageAlignment
<TITLE TJvWizardImageAlignment type>
Summary
  Defines possible alignments for wizard images.
Description
  TJvWizardImageAlignment is used by JvWizardDrawImage to define the horizontal alignment of the image
  it draws.
See Also
  JvWizardDrawImage, TJvWizardImageLayout

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageAlignment.iaLeft
  Align image to the left.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageAlignment.iaRight
  Align image to the right.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageAlignment.iaCenter
  Align image to the horizontal center.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageAlignment.iaStretch
  Stretch image horizontally.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageLayout
<TITLE TJvWizardImageLayout type>
Summary
  Defines possible vertical alignment of wizard images.
Description
  TJvWizardImageLayout is used by JvWizardDrawImage to define the vertical alignment of the image it
  draws.
See Also
  JvWizardDrawImage, TJvWizardImageAlignment

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageLayout.ilTop
  Align image to the top.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageLayout.ilBottom
  Align image to the bottom.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageLayout.ilCenter
  Align image to the vertical center.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageLayout.ilStretch
  Stretch image vertically.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageLayout.ilTile
  Tile image across client area.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardImageLeftRight
<TITLE TJvWizardImageLeftRight type>
Summary
  Defines a subrange of TJvWizardImageAlignment containing iaLeft and iaRight.
Description
  TJvWizardImageLeftRight is a subrange of TJvWizardImageAlignment.
See Also
  JvWizardDrawImage, TJvWizardImageAlignment

